{
  "stem": "8359.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was during already, that was the night, the winter of 1940.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was then 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were predicting a snowstorm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I went to bed that night, and I said a prayer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, dear God, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] let me wake up in the morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Let there be no snow and no Nazis.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He granted me one wish, no snow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, you'd like to know, why snow?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What's so bad about snow?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because people, kids that I used to go to school with-- I mean, I didn't go to school with, but we grew up together, next door, played, you know--",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kids don't know prejudice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kids are taught by their parents, or racism, what they call racism today.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They take a rock, and wrap the snow around it and throw it at you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Gentile",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's the pre-war years I'm talking-- well, this was an incident.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was always anti-Semitism in Poland, always.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah we played together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, kids get into fights.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was always zyd, zyd, zyd, they called us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is the Jew for-- and other words that I wouldn't even know how to translate into English.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not only did we hear, but we had some [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] proof, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, you can ask me how.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, my city that I came from, we were very close to the German border.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think we must have been about 15 miles from Auschwitz, which was Oswiecim in Polish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Auschwitz--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--was Oswiecim in Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that's the region that I came from.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when Hitler came into power-- I can't go back that far-- but I'm talking about mid '30s, already closer, maybe '37, '38.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
